#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.32"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.32:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.32:0.2"
msgid "4. Upālivagga"
msgstr "4. With Upāli"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 32. Pātimokkhaṭṭhapanāsutta → pāṭimokkhaṭṭhāpanasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an10.32:0.3"
msgid "32. Pātimokkhaṭṭhapanāsutta"
msgstr "32. Suspending the Recitation of the Monastic Code"

# BB has “suspend the patimokkha”, which, although literal, gives quite the wrong impression. It is the recital that is suspended, not the rules!
#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.71"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.32:1.1"
msgid "“Kati nu kho, bhante, pātimokkhaṭṭhapanā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, how many grounds are there to suspend the recitation of the monastic "
"code?”"

msgctxt "an10.32:1.2"
msgid "“Dasa kho, upāli, pātimokkhaṭṭhapanā."
msgstr ""
"“Upāli, there are ten grounds to suspend the recitation of the monastic code."

msgctxt "an10.32:1.3"
msgid "Katame dasa?"
msgstr "What ten?"

msgctxt "an10.32:1.4"
msgid ""
"Pārājiko tassaṃ parisāyaṃ nisinno hoti, pārājikakathā vippakatā hoti, "
"anupasampanno tassaṃ parisāyaṃ nisinno hoti, anupasampannakathā vippakatā "
"hoti, sikkhaṃ paccakkhātako tassaṃ parisāyaṃ nisinno hoti, sikkhaṃ "
"paccakkhātakakathā vippakatā hoti, paṇḍako tassaṃ parisāyaṃ nisinno hoti, "
"paṇḍakakathā vippakatā hoti, bhikkhunidūsako tassaṃ parisāyaṃ nisinno hoti, "
"bhikkhunidūsakakathā vippakatā hoti—"
msgstr ""
"A mendicant who has committed an expulsion offense is sitting in the "
"assembly. A discussion about whether someone has committed an expulsion "
"offense is unfinished. A person who is not fully ordained is sitting in the "
"assembly. A discussion about whether someone is fully ordained or not is "
"unfinished. Someone who has rejected the training is sitting in the "
"assembly. A discussion about whether someone has rejected the training or "
"not is unfinished. A eunuch is sitting in the assembly. A discussion about "
"whether someone is a eunuch is unfinished. A raper of nuns is sitting in the "
"assembly. A discussion about whether or not someone is a raper of nuns is "
"unfinished."

msgctxt "an10.32:1.5"
msgid "ime kho, upāli, dasa pātimokkhaṭṭhapanā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the ten grounds to suspend the recitation of the monastic code.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.32:1.6"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
